  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK789">
<l>naṭpiṟku vīṟṟirukkai yāteṉil koṭpiṉṟi</l>
<l>yollumvā yūṉṟu nilai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Friendship may be said to be on its throne when it possesses the power of supporting one at all times and under all circumstances, (in the practice or virtue and wealth).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
